701241f-a.title: Bronx: Henry Hudson Parkway - 232nd Street (West)
701241f-a.text:
Henry Hudson Parkway (Spuyten Duyvil Parkway), south from West 232nd Street. The large apartment house, in the center, is the Hudson Gardens,
at the S.E. corner of West 230th Street.
May 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.

701242f-a.title: Bronx: Henry Hudson Parkway - 232nd Street (West)
701242f-a.text:
Henry Hudson Parkway (Spuyten Duyvil Parkway), at the N.W. corner of West 232nd Street, showing the south end of Seton Hospital. The view is
in a northerly direction from West 231st Street.
May 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
